npc1: This is as far as I can take you. Beyond this gate is the thing that runs all of it.
npc1: Before you face it, I have to be sure you actually understand what you're fighting — not just how to swing at it.
npc1: So one last set of questions. There is no skipping this one. Answer them all correctly and the gate opens.
npc1: Miss one and that's fine — we go again until it's clear. This lesson matters more than the fight ever will.
